WEBVTT

00:01:27.491 --> 00:01:30.504
Most of them are man-made,
and we cannot blame God."

00:01:31.533 --> 00:01:34.134
So he asked, "Why does he let it happen?

00:01:34.158 --> 00:01:35.314
He could stop it."

00:01:35.859 --> 00:01:37.009
And I said ...

00:01:37.973 --> 00:01:40.021
"Yes he could, yes he could,

00:01:40.045 --> 00:01:42.943
but he sent us here as change agents,

00:01:42.967 --> 00:01:45.588
light of the world, salt of the earth,

00:01:45.612 --> 00:01:46.876
and we are failing."

00:01:48.839 --> 00:01:52.404
Africa has had a mixed affair
with organized religion,

00:01:52.428 --> 00:01:55.340
with both positive
and negative consequences.

